<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">一、  女声独唱《好日子》                                                                        车行词  李昕曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                  《采茶曲舞》                                                                              浙江民歌</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                     演唱：赵娜</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、  男高音独唱《阳光路上》                                               甲丁 王晓岭词  张宏光曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                      《和是我们共唱的歌》                            石顺义 吴立生词  王咏梅曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                        演唱：张向华（文化部优秀剧目展演获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、  二胡独奏《战马奔腾》                                                                              陈耀星曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                         演奏：蒋倩（全国民族器乐邀请赛获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、  男低音独唱《滚滚长江东逝水》             电视剧《三国演义》主题曲 谷建芬曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                      </span>《走进辉煌》                                                             纪联祥词 刘聪曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                      演唱：赵健</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、  女声独唱《月亮代表我的心》                                                         孙仪词 汤尼曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                  </span>《我只在乎你》                                                             慎芝词 黄铭源曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                   演唱：王紫菲（中华社会救助基金会形象大使）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">六、  男声独唱《儿行千里》                                                                车行词 戚建波曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                  </span>《卓玛》                                                                      真知和秋加措词曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                      演唱：尤龙</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">七、  笛子独奏《扬鞭催马运粮忙》                                                                 魏显忠曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                            演奏：丁晓逵（CCTV民乐大赛获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、  男声四重唱《菊花台》                                     方文山词  周杰伦曲  王志信改编</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                      </span>《少林，少林》                                              电影《少林寺》主题曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                      </span>《弹起我心爱的土琵琶》                          电影《铁道游击队》插曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                             演唱：张向华、肖笑、刘松焘、赵健</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">九、  女高音独唱《大漠深处》                                             音乐剧《复兴之路》插曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                      </span>《青春舞曲》                                                                  维吾尔族民歌</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                   演唱：谢琳（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十、    男女声二重唱《紫藤花》                                   </span><span style="font-size: medium;">             </span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: medium;">王泉 韩伟词</span><span style="font-size: medium;">  施光南曲</span></span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                            </span>《告别时刻》            Lucio Quarantotto词 Francesco Sartori曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                          演唱：谢琳、张向华</span></p>
